title: RSW aims to increase international routes
text:
Lee County, RSW hope to lure international visitors with increased international routes Adelie Pojzman-Pontay 12:43 PM, Sep 10, 2015 1:06 PM, Sep 10, 2015 Travelers make their way through Southwest Florida International Airport on Tuesday, May 12, 2015. Scott McIntyre/Staff Scott McIntyre   Show Caption Previous Next 
Lee County Port Authority recently approved a new budget for a program to attract more international flights to Southwest Florida International Airport. 
Full story available to subscribers only.
